  <h1 class="gd-h1">How to Choose a Heliski Operator</h1>
  <p class="gd-lede">The operators worth your money share three things: <strong>IFMGA/UIAGM-certified guides</strong>, a serious and documented safety system, and pricing built on <strong>guaranteed vertical feet</strong> rather than flight time. Get those right and the rest of the decision becomes simple. Everything below is the due-diligence checklist we walk every guest through before they book &mdash; and you can always ask us directly via <a href="/about">about us</a> or browse <a href="/packages">the packages</a> to see what good looks like.</p>
</div></section>
